graph LR
    A[开始] --> B[定义搜索空间]
    B --> C[选择初始采样点]
    C --> D[评估目标函数]
    D --> E[训练代理模型<br>(高斯过程回归)]
    E --> F{达到终止条件?}
    F -- 否 --> G[使用预期改进<br>选择下一个采样点]
    G --> D
    F -- 是 --> H[结束，返回最佳观测]

# Simulated gold mining example: 
# We will simulate a gold distribution along a line (1D space)
np.random.seed(42)  # for reproducibility

# This is our black-box function we are trying to optimize.
def true_gold_distribution(x):
    """Simulated true gold distribution."""
    return np.sin(3*x) + np.cos(5*x) + np.random.normal(0, 0.2, size=x.shape)

# Define the Gaussian Process model
kernel = Matern(nu=2.5)
# 在高斯过程（GP）模型中，核（kernel）是一种函数，用于衡量输入空间中两点之间的相似度。
# 不同的核函数会导致GP有不同的平滑度和波动性。
# Matérn核是一种常用的核函数，它是一类可以通过参数调整其平滑性的核。
# nu=2.5 参数控制了核的平滑程度，不同的 nu 值会导致模型具有不同的平滑性质。
gp = GaussianProcessRegressor(kernel=kernel, n_restarts_optimizer=9)
# 这是高斯过程回归（Gaussian Process Regression, GPR）模型的实例。在贝叶斯优化中，它被用作代理模型来近似未知的目标函数。
# gp 不是一个黑盒函数，而是一个通过已知数据点训练出来的模型，用来预测任意位置的函数值及其不确定性（预测的标准差）。

# Initial random samples
initial_samples = np.random.uniform(0, 2, 5).reshape(-1, 1)
initial_observations = true_gold_distribution(initial_samples)

# Update the model with initial samples
gp.fit(initial_samples, initial_observations)

def expected_improvement(X, X_sample, Y_sample, gp, xi=0.01):
    # 这个函数计算了在每个可能的新采样点上的预期改进量。
    # 它使用 gp 模型的预测及其不确定性来估算每个点的改进潜力，然后选择具有最大预期改进值的点作为下一个采样点。
    mu, sigma = gp.predict(X, return_std=True)
    mu_sample = gp.predict(X_sample)
    mu_sample_opt = np.max(mu_sample)

    with np.errstate(divide='warn'):
        imp = mu - mu_sample_opt - xi
        Z = imp / sigma
        ei = imp * norm.cdf(Z) + sigma * norm.pdf(Z)
        ei[sigma == 0.0] = 0.0  # 确保 sigma 是一维的，这样布尔索引才能正常工作

    # 这里返回的是一个数组，它包含了每个候选点的预期改进值
    # 也就是在一个x轴上的每个点的预期改进值，这个值越大，说明这个点越有可能是最优点
    # 一般来说这个数组包含了很多点，我们只需要选择其中的一个点作为下一个采样点
    # 数组的长度取决于X的长度
    return ei

def propose_location(acquisition, X_sample, Y_sample, gp):
    # 这个函数使用 expected_improvement 函数来确定下一个最佳的采样位置。
    # 它通过计算所有候选点的预期改进值，并选择具有最大值的点作为下一个采样点。
    X = np.linspace(0, 2, 400).reshape(-1, 1)
    # 这里的acquisition是一个函数，它接受X，X_sample，Y_sample，gp作为参数，并返回一个数组。在这个例子中，它是expected_improvement函数。
    acquisition_values = acquisition(X, X_sample, Y_sample, gp)
    
    # 这里返回的是具有最大预期改进值的点，坐标轴上是 x 值
    return X[np.argmax(acquisition_values)]

在每次迭代中，选定的新采样点（通过 propose_location 函数确定）会被用来评估目标函数，然后将这个新的数据点（位置和对应的函数值）加入到已有的数据集中。

然后，gp 模型会使用所有当前可用的数据点来进行重新训练（更新）。

通过这种方式，每一次迭代后，代理模型都会变得更加准确地反映真实的目标函数，从而更有效地指导下一个采样点的选择。

# 可视化高斯过程模型的更新
X_sample = initial_samples.copy()
Y_sample = initial_observations.copy()

iteration_num = 10

for i in range(iteration_num):
    gp.fit(X_sample, Y_sample)
    X = np.linspace(0, 2, 400).reshape(-1, 1)
    mu, std = gp.predict(X, return_std=True)
    
    # Calculate and display the mean squared error
    mse = mean_squared_error(true_gold_distribution(X), mu)


    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 5))
    plt.plot(X, mu, 'k', lw=1.5, zorder=9)
    plt.fill_between(X.ravel(), mu - 1.96 * std, mu + 1.96 * std, alpha=0.2, color='k')
    plt.scatter(X_sample, Y_sample, c='r', s=50, zorder=10, edgecolors='k', label='Observed Data')

    # put the value of MSE in the plot, and set the position of the text, the position should be below the true gold distribution and next to the vertical line
    # Add MSE text below the true gold distribution and next to the vertical line
    plt.text(0.5, -1.5, f"MSE: {mse:.2f}", color='blue', fontsize=12, ha='center', va='bottom')

    if i < iteration_num - 1: # 最后一次迭代后不再添加新的点
        X_next = propose_location(expected_improvement, X_sample, Y_sample, gp)
        Y_next = true_gold_distribution(X_next.reshape(-1, 1))
        plt.scatter(X_next, Y_next, c='g', s=100, zorder=10, edgecolors='k', label='Next Point')

    if i < iteration_num - 1: # 最后一次迭代后不再添加新的点
        plt.title(f"GP Model After {i+1} Iteration(s)")
        plt.xlabel("X")
        plt.ylabel("Y")
        plt.legend()
    else:
        plt.title(f"{i+1} Iteration(s) - The End")
        plt.xlabel("X")
        plt.ylabel("Y")
        plt.legend()
    
    
    plt.show()

    X_sample = np.vstack((X_sample, X_next))
    Y_sample = np.vstack((Y_sample, Y_next))

In [ ]:
# Re-initialize the samples and Gaussian Process for a fresh start
X_sample = initial_samples
Y_sample = initial_observations
gp.fit(X_sample, Y_sample)

# Perform and plot each iteration
n_iter = 5
for i in range(n_iter):
    # Find the point of maximum expected improvement
    X_next = propose_location(expected_improvement, X_sample, Y_sample, gp)

    # Sample the next point and update the model
    Y_next = true_gold_distribution(X_next.reshape(-1, 1))
    X_sample = np.vstack((X_sample, X_next.reshape(-1, 1)))
    Y_sample = np.vstack((Y_sample, Y_next))
    gp.fit(X_sample, Y_sample)

    # Plot the surrogate function, the observed points, and the next sampling location
    plt.figure(figsize=(14, 7))
    mu, std = gp.predict(X, return_std=True)
    plt.plot(X, mu, 'b-', lw=2, label='Surrogate model prediction')
    plt.fill_between(X.ravel(), mu - 1.96 * std, mu + 1.96 * std, alpha=0.1)
    plt.plot(X_sample, Y_sample, 'kx', mew=2, label='Samples')
    plt.axvline(x=X_next, ls='--', c='k', lw=1, label='Next sampling location')
    plt.title(f"Surrogate Model and Samples after Iteration {i+1}")
    plt.xlabel("Location")
    plt.ylabel("Gold quantity")
    plt.legend()
    plt.show()

我：

当我们在使用贝叶斯优化的时候，是不是我们对需要优化的对象（真实的函数），其实是不知道他的真实状态的，我们只能对她以黑盒的形式进行对待，也就是说，当我对黑盒进行输入时，我只能得到黑盒的输出，但是不知道盒黑本身的公式。所以我才需要用贝叶斯优化去寻找到对黑盒最match的函数式

回答：

完全正确！在贝叶斯优化中，我们通常处理的是所谓的“黑盒”函数，这是因为我们不知道这个函数的内部工作原理或它的解析形式。我们的目标是找到这个未知函数的最大值或最小值，但我们只能通过在不同的输入点进行采样来了解它的行为。每次采样都可能耗费昂贵的资源或时间，这就是为什么贝叶斯优化非常宝贵的原因，因为它试图智能地选择采样点以最小化这些成本。

代理模型（在我们例子中是高斯过程模型）被用来近似真实的未知函数。通过观察代理模型的预测和预测不确定性，贝叶斯优化利用收集函数（如预期改进）来决定下一个最有价值的采样点。随着更多数据点的采集，代理模型被更新，以期更好地近似真实的未知函数。这个过程持续进行，直到满足某种停止标准，比如达到预算限制、迭代次数或收敛到满意的解。

总的来说，贝叶斯优化是一种用于全局优化未知或昂贵评价函数的方法，特别是在无法获得函数解析形式时。

生成100次迭代¶

# Initial random samples
np.random.seed(42)
initial_samples = np.random.uniform(0, 2, 5).reshape(-1, 1)
initial_observations = true_gold_distribution(initial_samples)

# Initialize the model and samples for a fresh Bayesian Optimization process
X_sample = initial_samples
Y_sample = initial_observations
gp.fit(X_sample, Y_sample)

# Create a list to store the images
images = []

# Perform and plot each iteration, along with evaluations
n_iter = 100
threshold_mse = 0.1  # Define the threshold for "good" model accuracy

for i in range(n_iter):
    # Find the point of maximum expected improvement
    X_next = propose_location(expected_improvement, X_sample, Y_sample, gp)

    # Sample the next point and update the model
    Y_next = true_gold_distribution(X_next.reshape(-1, 1))
    X_sample = np.vstack((X_sample, X_next.reshape(-1, 1)))
    Y_sample = np.vstack((Y_sample, Y_next))
    gp.fit(X_sample, Y_sample)
    
    # Calculate and display the mean squared error
    mse = mean_squared_error(y_true, mu)

    # Evaluate the model's current state by plotting and calculating MSE
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(14, 7))  # Define the figure
    mu, std = gp.predict(X, return_std=True)
    
    plt.plot(X, mu, 'b-', lw=2, label='Surrogate model prediction')
    plt.fill_between(X.ravel(), mu - 1.96 * std, mu + 1.96 * std, alpha=0.5)
    
    plt.plot(X_sample, Y_sample, 'kx', mew=2, label='Samples')
    plt.axvline(x=X_next, ls='--', c='k', lw=1, label='Next sampling location')
    
    plt.plot(X, y_true, 'y--', lw=2, label='True gold distribution')
    
    plt.title(f"Surrogate Model and Samples after Iteration {i+1}")
    plt.xlabel("Location")
    plt.ylabel("Gold quantity")
    
    # put the value of MSE in the plot, and set the position of the text, the position should be below the true gold distribution and next to the vertical line
    # Add MSE text below the true gold distribution and next to the vertical line
    plt.text(X_next + 0.05, min(y_true) - 0.25, f"MSE: {mse:.4f}", fontsize=12)    
    
    plt.legend()

    # Save the current plot as an image
    plt.savefig(f"/Users/gan-m2/Machine-Learning-Engineering-for-Production/3-Machine Learning Modeling Pipelines in Production/W1/Bayesian Optimation/iteration_{i+1}.png")
    
    # Close the current plot
    plt.close()

    print(f"Iteration {i+1}: Mean Squared Error (MSE) between the surrogate model and true function: {mse:.4f}")

    # reach the end of the loop print the message
    if i == n_iter - 1:
        print("The maximum number of iterations has been reached.")

import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn.gaussian_process import GaussianProcessRegressor
from sklearn.gaussian_process.kernels import Matern
from scipy.stats import norm
from sklearn.metrics import mean_squared_error

# 假设已定义：true_gold_distribution, expected_improvement, propose_location

np.random.seed(42)
initial_samples = np.random.uniform(0, 2, 5).reshape(-1, 1)
initial_observations = true_gold_distribution(initial_samples)

kernel = Matern(nu=2.5)
gp = GaussianProcessRegressor(kernel=kernel, n_restarts_optimizer=9)
gp.fit(initial_samples, initial_observations)

X_sample = np.copy(initial_samples)
Y_sample = np.copy(initial_observations)

X = np.linspace(0, 2, 400).reshape(-1, 1)
y_true = true_gold_distribution(X)

n_iter = 100
threshold_mse = 0.1  # 定义“好”的模型准确性阈值

# Temporary variables for the previous and current sample points
X_prev = None
Y_prev = None


for i in range(n_iter):
    X_next = propose_location(expected_improvement, X_sample, Y_sample, gp)
    Y_next = true_gold_distribution(X_next.reshape(-1, 1))

    if i > 0:  # 从第二轮开始，保存上一轮的X_next作为last_X_next
        last_X_next = X_sample[-2]

    X_sample = np.vstack((X_sample, X_next))
    Y_sample = np.vstack((Y_sample, Y_next))
    gp.fit(X_sample, Y_sample)

    mu, std = gp.predict(X, return_std=True)
    mse = mean_squared_error(y_true, mu)

    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(14, 7))
    plt.plot(X, mu, 'b-', lw=2, label='Surrogate model prediction')
    plt.fill_between(X.ravel(), mu - 1.96 * std, mu + 1.96 * std, alpha=0.1)
    if i > 0:  # Plot the previous point if it exists
        plt.scatter(X_prev, Y_prev, color='green', s=100, label='Previous sample')
    plt.scatter(X_next, Y_next, color='red', s=100, label='Current sample')  # Plot the current point
    plt.plot(X, y_true, 'y--', lw=2, label='True gold distribution')
    plt.title(f"Surrogate Model and Samples after Iteration {i+1}")
    plt.xlabel("Location")
    plt.ylabel("Gold quantity")

    # Add MSE text below the true gold distribution and next to the vertical line
    plt.text(X_next + 0.05, min(y_true) - 0.25, f"MSE: {mse:.4f}", fontsize=12)
    
    plt.legend()

    # Save the current plot as an image
    plt.savefig(f"/Users/gan-m2/Machine-Learning-Engineering-for-Production/3-Machine Learning Modeling Pipelines in Production/W1/Bayesian Optimation/iteration_{i+1}.png")

    plt.close()
    # Update the temporary variables for the next iteration
    X_prev, Y_prev = X_next, Y_next

    print(f"Iteration {i+1}: Mean Squared Error (MSE): {mse:.4f}")

import plotly.graph_objects as go
import numpy as np
from sklearn.gaussian_process import GaussianProcessRegressor
from sklearn.gaussian_process.kernels import Matern
from scipy.stats import norm
from sklearn.metrics import mean_squared_error

# 假定 true_gold_distribution, expected_improvement, propose_location 等函数已经定义

# 设置随机种子以确保可重现性
np.random.seed(42)

# 初始化随机采样点
initial_samples = np.random.uniform(0, 2, 5).reshape(-1, 1)
initial_observations = true_gold_distribution(initial_samples)

# 初始化高斯过程模型
kernel = Matern(nu=2.5)
gp = GaussianProcessRegressor(kernel=kernel, n_restarts_optimizer=9)
gp.fit(initial_samples, initial_observations)

# 重新初始化 X_sample 和 Y_sample 为贝叶斯优化过程的起始点
X_sample = np.copy(initial_samples)
Y_sample = np.copy(initial_observations)

# 定义黄金分布搜索空间
X = np.linspace(0, 2, 400).reshape(-1, 1)
y_true = true_gold_distribution(X)

# 创建初始图表
fig = go.Figure(
    data=[
        go.Scatter(x=X.ravel(), y=y_true.ravel(), mode='lines', name='True Gold Distribution'),
        go.Scatter(x=initial_samples.ravel(), y=initial_observations.ravel(), mode='markers', name='Initial Samples')
    ],
    layout=go.Layout(
        title="Bayesian Optimization in Action",
        updatemenus=[dict(
            type="buttons",
            buttons=[dict(label="Play",
                          method="animate",
                          args=[None, {"frame": {"duration": 500, "redraw": True}, "fromcurrent": True}])])]
    ),
    frames=[]
)

# 迭代并构建每一帧
for i in range(100):
    # 计算下一个采样点
    X_next = propose_location(expected_improvement, X_sample, Y_sample, gp)
    
    # 采样并更新模型
    Y_next = true_gold_distribution(X_next.reshape(-1, 1))
    X_sample = np.vstack((X_sample, X_next))
    Y_sample = np.vstack((Y_sample, Y_next))
    gp.fit(X_sample, Y_sample)

    # 计算模型预测和MSE
    mu, std = gp.predict(X, return_std=True)
    mse = mean_squared_error(y_true, mu)

    # 创建当前帧
    frame = go.Frame(
        data=[
            go.Scatter(x=X.ravel(), y=mu.ravel(), mode='lines', name=f'Surrogate Prediction (Iteration {i+1})'),
            go.Scatter(x=X_sample.ravel(), y=Y_sample.ravel(), mode='markers', name=f'Samples (Iteration {i+1})')
        ],
        layout=go.Layout(title=f"Iteration: {i+1}, MSE: {mse:.4f}")
    )
    fig.frames.append(frame)

# 展示动画
fig.show()
